    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1086">
<l>koṭumpuruvaṅ kōṭā maṟaippi ṉaṭuṅkañar</l>
<l>ceyyala maṉṉivaḷ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Her eyes will cause (me) no trembling sorrow, if they are properly hidden by her cruel arched eye-brows.</l>
            </lg>
